title: 59: OBITCH king tit!
description:
Well hello Geoffs! This week your favorite moirologists are back to bring you some cursed graves and learn all about the dangerous life of a magician! We’ve got an obituary with some petty last words, one for a goodfella, and so much more, including dumb.ass.criminalllllls of course! 



New episodes come out every (day of week) for free, with 1-week early access for Wondery+ subscribers.


SEE US LIVE IN IRVINE ON AUGUST 4TH: https://tinyurl.com/3fvwbsnz



Follow along online: @obitchuarypod on Twitter & Instagram.
